replies.body:
Yeah, I'd also love to experiment around with runes... shame it feels impossible and discouraged :(
I only have 2 rune pages and already had to squeeze 3 playstyles into them. With the mastery system I could get away with buying 0 pages cause they were only stats and the mastery pages were free. Now, I'll have to grind half a year and spend exclusively on rune pages in that time to make the system comfortable (at least 1 page for each playstyle/favorite champ) and THEN I will be able to start actual experimentation... Shame, I was so hyped and I still feel hyped for the possibility, but my enthusiasm is just killed off completely as I feel like I'm forced to grind exclusively with the 3 playstyles (2 champions) that I was able to fit into my 2 rune pages, and avoid playing with anyone else (as they can't yet have their proper rune pages)...
Feels bad, man{{sticker:cass-cry}}
